00:02:37,058 --> 00:02:43,241
a solidity to them. We were actually going to do, we're trying to do, hidden line vector,

54
00:02:43,341 --> 00:02:48,283
which is a very tricky kind of graphics. And we could do about, on our scope, it wasn't

