134
00:06:48,659 --> 00:06:53,781
I wanted to make 10 or 20-hour cinematic story-based games.

135
00:06:53,901 --> 00:06:57,543
And I was in a world, right, one quarter got you three minutes.

136
00:06:57,603 --> 00:06:59,685
It doesn't get you this, whatever it is.

137
00:07:01,248 --> 00:07:06,590
