00:13:00,135 --> 00:13:02,857
own design document I have is from the website.

286
00:13:05,161 --> 00:13:12,023
So for controls, we'd actually done for Quack, one of the versions, we'd done an industrial

287
00:13:12,143 --> 00:13:13,523
strength touchscreen.

