00:42:00,132 --> 00:42:09,118
the press 20 plus years ago that you were unexpectedly a detriment to the major havoc project

825
00:42:09,178 --> 00:42:14,541
because you were such a good play tester the game was tuned too high in the arcade. I read that in

826
00:42:14,581 --> 00:42:19,124
an article and I don't know if that was someone being, they were talking about you in the context

827
00:42:19,144 --> 00:42:19,924
of Marvel Madness.

828
00:42:20,165 --> 00:42:20,445
Really?

829
00:42:20,905 --> 00:42:21,105
Yes.

830
00:42:21,675 --> 00:42:24,176
At the arcade show last year,

831
00:42:24,236 --> 00:42:27,137
the Gravatar team said I almost took the team down,

832
00:42:27,937 --> 00:42:30,717
actually, because yeah, I was the in-house play tester,

833
00:42:30,918 --> 00:42:32,158
and I thought it was much too easy.

834
00:42:33,438 --> 00:42:35,379
It's a good lesson in usability for everybody involved,

835
00:42:35,399 --> 00:42:35,919
let me tell you that.

836
00:42:35,959 --> 00:42:37,479
I haven't heard that about Major Havoc, though.

837
00:42:38,259 --> 00:42:40,520
We just had to kill the player so darn fast was the thing.

838
00:42:40,560 --> 00:42:43,260
I mean, if the game time play averages

839
00:42:43,300 --> 00:42:45,681
weren't three minutes or less, it was unsaleable,

840
00:42:45,841 --> 00:42:48,302
and Major Havoc, because it was sort of a platformer

841
00:42:48,342 --> 00:42:50,402
in some respects, was more like a four-minute game.

842
00:42:53,664 --> 00:42:57,228
Question about all the fall on ports of Marble Madness 7.

843
00:42:57,268 --> 00:42:59,910
Were you involved in any of those, bringing Marble Madness to any of the platforms?

844
00:42:59,990 --> 00:43:03,434
And did it have any kind of a different, was the contrast really notable to you?

845
00:43:03,494 --> 00:43:05,236
No, I wasn't involved in any of those.

846
00:43:05,276 --> 00:43:07,838
It's really a shame that they couldn't have used trackballs.

847
00:43:08,219 --> 00:43:10,221
It's not really such the same game as a joystick.

848
00:43:10,261 --> 00:43:12,223
But now that we have the tablets and things,

849
00:43:12,683 --> 00:43:15,026
we might be able to use the gyros in there to do something well.

