00:43:20,333 --> 00:43:23,576
and ask if I wanted to convert it to other smartphones, and I noticed they'd ripped my

852
00:43:23,616 --> 00:43:24,497
credit out of the game.

853
00:43:25,418 --> 00:43:30,142
And my question was, if I did the project, would I be responsible for ripping out my

