00:44:14,210 --> 00:44:19,594
between the track ball and the control panel is just perfect enough for a seven-year-old

864
00:44:20,014 --> 00:44:22,636
to get his middle finger stuck right in there?

865
00:44:22,776 --> 00:44:28,600
Now, you should have played Dave Toyer's game where it was a real bowling ball without holes

866
00:44:28,660 --> 00:44:32,582
because you could get the entire side of your hand in there.

867
00:44:34,464 --> 00:44:35,885
You owe me some Band-Aid money.

