00:44:58,879 --> 00:45:05,241
on Marble Madness, working with, oh, he'll kill me because I'm forgetting his name, Haley,

871
00:45:05,321 --> 00:45:06,561
who worked on, um,

872
00:45:07,338 --> 00:45:10,339
Paperboy and a couple other very famous games.

873
00:45:11,140 --> 00:45:13,160
And they, Mike Halley, sorry.

874
00:45:13,540 --> 00:45:15,361
And they took a very different approach.

875
00:45:15,401 --> 00:45:17,821
They thought that the sort of abstract look was hurting them.

