00:45:50,801 --> 00:45:51,622
A case where I...

890
00:45:52,363 --> 00:45:54,465
Too many unique tiles for the background?

891
00:45:54,605 --> 00:45:57,347
You know, I kind of just worked and I didn't think too hard about it.

892
00:45:58,909 --> 00:46:00,210
I wish I had a better answer than that.

893
00:46:00,802 --> 00:46:05,564
I should have done more play fields than that. I have really a mystery looking back why that

894
00:46:05,724 --> 00:46:11,648
is all that is in the game. When we could have run, you know, three months longer and

895
00:46:11,688 --> 00:46:16,070
had an eight-minute game and maybe not dropped out of first place in the arcades after six

896
00:46:16,110 --> 00:46:16,350
weeks.

897
00:46:16,951 --> 00:46:17,151
Thank you.

