903
00:46:39,805 --> 00:46:40,786
It was a great moment.

904
00:46:42,127 --> 00:46:42,387
Thank you.

905
00:46:43,187 --> 00:46:44,188
Well, oh, yes.

906
00:46:45,129 --> 00:46:47,811
Just as a, you know, playing it a lot,

