00:48:08,343 --> 00:48:10,704
hardware. We could have just typed it in and seen it live.

935
00:48:11,525 --> 00:48:11,745
Yeah.

936
00:48:14,087 --> 00:48:16,949
But, but other things like, you know, the, I don't know,

